data.description:
ENJOY OUTDOOR LIVING EVERYDAY AT THIS IMMACULATE TOLL BROTHERS POTOMAC SPANISH HOME WITH LOTS OF UPGRADES AT STERLING GROVE GOLF & COUNTRY CLUB IN BEAUTIFUL SURPRISE, ARIZONA!  NO BUILD TIME WAIT!  INSTANT SAVINGS WITH SOLAR!

THIS AMAZING HOME IS LOCATED IN THE AGE-RESTRICTED 55+ COMMUNITY AT STERLING GROVE.  

NESTLED ON AN OVERSIZED LOT WITH AN EXTENDED DRIVEWAY, THERE ARE SO MANY UPGRADES IN THE INTERIOR AND EXTERIOR OF THE HOME! JUST THE RIGHT AMOUNT OF SQUARE FOOTAGE IN 2,045 WHICH IS NOT TOO MUCH OR TOO LITTLE! AS YOU ENTER THE FOYER, YOU WILL FIND AN APPEALING HERRINGBONE TILE DESIGN WITH UPGRADED TILE THROUGHOUT THE HOUSE WHICH WAS DONE AFTER THE HOME WAS PURCHASED! SPACIOUS GREAT ROOM OPEN FLOOR PLAN, PRIVATE OFFICE WITH DOUBLE BARN DOORS, CUSTOM BUILT-IN DESK AND CUSTOM CABINETS. SHUTTER WINDOW TREATMENTS IN THE MAIN AREA AND RECESSED LIGHTING THROUGHOUT THE HOME!

GORGEOUS KITCHEN WITH TILED ISLAND AND BACKSPLASH, QUARTZ COUNTERTOPS, SOFT CLOSE CABINETS w/HARDWARE, STAINLESS STEEL KITCHEN AID APPLIANCES WITH BUILT-IN MICROWAVE, GAS RANGE AND ELECTRIC OVEN! 

WAIT! THERE IS MUCH MORE! LARGE MASTER BEDROOM WITH A PATIO DOOR THAT LEADS YOU OUT TO THE HOT TUB TO RELAX AND UNWIND! SPA LIKE MASTER BATHROOM WITH HIS & HER SINKS, BEAUTIFUL TILED SHOWER WITH RAINFALL SHOWER HEAD! MASTER BEDROOM IS EQUIPPED WITH CUSTOM CLOSETS THAT GIVES IT EVEN MORE STYLE WITH CHARACTER!

ENSUITE FOR YOUR GUESTS IS SPACIOUS WITH BUILT-IN CLOSET SHELVES, BATHROOM WITH UPGRADED CABINETS AND A WALK-IN SHOWER.

LAUNDRY ROOM HAS CUSTOM CABINETS, UPGRADED ELECTROLUX WASHER AND DRYER WITH A WINE FRIDGE TO SIP WHILE DOING LAUNDRY!

EXTENDED GARAGE THAT HAS SPACE FOR YOUR GOLF CART! EPOXY GARAGE FLOORING, BUILT-IN CABINETS, EXTRA LIGHTING AND OUTLETS! SPRAY FOAM INSULATION IN GARAGE WALLS AND CEILING, SOFT WATER SYSTEM, AND TANKLESS WATER HEATER. PLENTY OF GARAGE WORK SPACE FOR YOUR HOBBIES!

GO OUTBACK TO ENJOY OUTDOOR LIVING AT IT'S FINEST!  SO MUCH SPACE TO ENTERTAIN FAMILY AND FRIENDS OR TO JUST RELAX BY YOURSELVES!

BACKAYARD IS ON AN OVERSIZED LOT! PERGOLA ATTACHED TO THE HOUSE, TRAVERTINE TILE, WATERFALL, GAS FIREPIT, THERAPUTIC SPA (HEATED AND PURCHASED IN 2022). LET'S GET COOKIN! BUILT-IN GAS GRILL AND BUILT-IN ELECTRIC SMOKER!

SOLAR WILL BE PAID OFF FROM THE SALE OF THE HOME.  INSTANT SAVINGS!

YOU'VE GOT TO SEE THIS ONE!  COME SEE FOR YOURSELF!

Community Information:
Sterling Grove Golf & Country Club is a Gated Community w/24 Hour Guard Post. Great Opportunity to Enjoy on a daily basis so many Wonderful Amenities and Beautiful Views of the White Tank Mountains, Lakes, Ponds and Gorgeous Greens on your Walks, Jogs, Bike Rides!

Amenities: TROON Managed Jack Nicklaus Design 18 Hole Golf Course, Tennis Courts, Pickleball Courts, Country Club, Swimming Pools, Fitness Center, Spa, Restaurants, and Much More!
